<p><span style=‘color: #e03e2d;‘><strong>3. Teacher Platforms and agree the teacher agreement</strong></span></p><p><strong>&nbsp; 3.1 How to use QQ (For teacher support from the school side)</strong></p><p>Link for downloading QQ (Chinese Version): <a href=‘https://im.qq.com/index.shtml‘ target=‘_blank‘ rel=‘noopener‘>https://im.qq.com/index.shtml</a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; 3.2 Skype (One of the teaching platform)</strong></p><p>Download link: <a href=‘https://www.skype.com/en/get-skype/‘ target=‘_blank‘ rel=‘noopener‘>https://www.skype.com/en/get-skype/</a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;3.3 How to use Classin(Main teaching platform we are using for online classes</strong><strong>，especially for kids</strong><strong>）</strong></p><p>Download link：<a href=‘https://www.eeo.cn/en/download.html‘ target=‘_blank‘ rel=‘noopener‘>https://www.eeo.cn/en/download.html</a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;3.4 How to use Portal system(Open schedule, Check bookings, Check records and comments)</strong></p><p>Login page of Portal System<strong>：</strong><a href=‘http://portal.tracyclass.com/login.php‘ target=‘_blank‘ rel=‘noopener‘>http://portal.tracyclass.com/login.php</a></p><p><span style=‘color: #e03e2d;‘><strong>Login details would be provided via email and on Skype under the following circumstances </strong></span></p><ul><li>Passed the demo video evaluation</li><li>Uploaded all the required documents(then you&rsquo;ll receive the login details within 2-3 working days)</li></ul><p><span style=‘text-decoration: underline; color: #000000;‘><strong>Click the link below to learn more on how to use teacher platforms including QQ, Skype, Classin, Portal System:</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;<a href=‘https://team.teacherrecord.cn/docs/view/52928466a9bebedc‘ target=‘_blank‘ rel=‘noopener‘>https://team.teacherrecord.cn/docs/view/52928466a9bebedc</a></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=‘color: #e03e2d;‘>&nbsp;<strong>3.42 Please download and read the Teacher Agreement carefully</strong></span>